The Requirements Planning, Manufacturing – Shop Floor, and Manufacturing PDM programs may only be used in order to access the features and functions of Capital Asset Management.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Manufacturing and Supply Chain Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Blend Management includes a restricted-use license for the JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Manufacturing Management module. The EnterpriseOne Manufacturing Management module may only be used to define bill of materials for chemicals used in the Blend Management additive operation.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Customer Relationship Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne In-Memory Sales Advisor
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for In-Memory Sales Advisor contains a restricted-use license for WebLogic Server Standard Edition. Use of WebLogic Server Standard Edition is limited to use with In-Memory Sales Advisor and may not be used or deployed for other purposes

A license for Financials includes a restricted-use of Oracle JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Real Estate Management, limited to lessee lease management features. Any usage of sales overage, expense participation or lessor lease management requires a full use license of Real Estate Management.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Customer Relationship Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Service Management includes a restricted-use license for the Contract and Service Billing, Requirements Planning, Manufacturing – Shop Floor, and Manufacturing – PDM programs. The Contract and Service Billing, Requirements Planning, Manufacturing – Shop Floor, and Manufacturing – PDM programs may only be used in order to access the features and functions Service Management.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Environment Accounting and Reporting
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Environment Accounting and Reporting includes a restricted-use of Oracle Data Integrator Enterprise Edition, solely for the purpose of extracting data from Environmental Accounting and Reporting application schemas in JD Edwards EnterpriseOne and integrating the data into the Oracle data model used by Environmental Accounting and Reporting in an Oracle data warehouse. Any customizations to the Environment Accounting and Reporting application or underlying schemes would require a full use license of Oracle Data Integrator Enterprise Edition.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Asset Lifecycle Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Rental Management includes a restricted-use license for the Contract and Service Billing programs. The Contract and Service Billing programs may only be used in order to access the features and functions of Rental Management.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Manufacturing and Supply Chain Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: "A license for Grower Management includes a restricted-use license for the JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Manufacturing Management program to define bills of materials for chemicals used in the Grower Management Spray operation. The license for Grower Management also includes a restricted-use license for the Blend Management program to use only the operations that are designated as ""Grower"" operations and the setup required to run the ""Grower"" operations."

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne In-Memory Planning Advisor
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for In-Memory Planning Advisor includes a restricted-use license for Oracle WebLogic Server Standard Edition. Use of WebLogic Server Standard Edition is limited to use with In-Memory Planning Advisor and may not be used or deployed for other purposes.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne In-Memory Project Portfolio Advisor
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for In-Memory Project Portfolio Advisor includes a restricted-use license for Oracle WebLogic Server Standard Edition. Use of WebLogic Server Standard Edition is limited to use with In-Memory Project Portfolio Advisor and may not be used or deployed for other purposes.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_product: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Human Capital Management
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Time and Labor
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Time and Labor includes a restricted-use license for JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Resources Assignments. The Resource Assignments program may only be used in order to manage and maintain crew definitions in the Resource Master Resource Assignments program and access features and functions when using time entry mobile applications. A license for Time and Labor includes a restricted-use license to Self-Service Human Resources. The restricted-use license is for the Time Entry Self Service Setup application, Time Entry Self Service Director applications, and Manager Delegates application. The Time Entry Self Service Setup application, Time Entry Self Service Director applications and Manage Delegates application may only be used to select and sequence time entry fields to display in the mobile time entry applications, enter, update, review, and approve timecards and to specify delegates when using the mobile time entry applications.

settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_component: JD Edwards EnterpriseOne Demand Scheduling Execution
settings_jde_restrictions.rtc_restriction: A license for Demand Scheduling Execution includes (i) a restricted-use license for the Warehouse Management program to use only Carton and Container definitions, Carton and Container Bill of Materials, Item and Pallet standard pack definitions, Standard Pack Carton Recommendations, Carton Reconciliation to Sales Order, Carton Reorganization and Inquiry and Label Number Processing and does not allow use of any location selection process, volume-based carton recommendation or movement confirmation and (ii) a restricted-use license for the Transportation Management program to use only Transportation Constants, Transportation Preferences, Shipment Creation, Shipment Approval, Shipment Confirmation, Transportation Shipment Confirmation, Seal Number processing, ASN processing and the Bill of Lading report and does not allow use of any rating and routing processing, load processing or inbound transportation processing.
